parameters: After delivering many painful bites, the baby crawls back
You stagger back to your apartment, doing your best to hold
your wounds shut. Your skin is burning, your head aches.
The adrenaline from the battle crashes.
The pain from all those bites begins to hit you in full.
You collapse just in front of your door.
You sit up against the doorframe, and inspect the damage.
The largest bite was on your chest. Another one is on your arm,
and another one on your hip.
Smaller Tooth marks on your neck. Scrapes on your back.\.\.
Nothing was spared.\.\. You look like you'be been gnawed on like
a chew toy.\.\. You feel like it, too.
You feel hard nubs growing all over your wounds.
You look at Clint's lifeless body. Even in death, the teeth
rash has continued to colonize his corpse.
Clint is beaming down at you with pride.
You feel your face and the top of your head. Gums and lips
part between your fingers at the top of your scalp.
You feel compelled to reach inside.\.\. Inside of your own head.
It feels damp, warm. You have your entire forearm in there.
You feel a new kind of gag reflex from inside your skull and pull
You scrape the back of your hand against dozens of
Teeth inside your head. Teeth inside your brain.
You feel far too many lips curl into a smile.
There's a little army guy figurine on the table.
Inside you find...\.\. an old \C[03]{Rifle}\C[00] and some \C[03]{Rifle Bullets}\C[0]!
